OL,3,CNew research highlights the best video
OL,4,Ccall backgrounds
OL,6,FITV News' David Harper explores all
OL,7,Fthe different type of virtual
OL,8,Fbackgrounds that researchers have said
OL,9,Fare associated with "Zoom fatigue"
OL,11,FUsing video or moving backgrounds
OL,12,Fduring Zoom calls can increase mental
OL,13,Fand physical tiredness during virtual
OL,14,Fmeetings, research suggests.
OL,16,FScientists said this is because,
OL,17,Funlike still images or blurred
OL,18,Fbackdrops, video backgrounds
OL,19,Fcontinuously present new information
OL,20,Fthat demand a person's attention and
OL,21,Fbrainpower.
