OL,3,CNew research highlights the best video
OL,4,Ccall backgrounds
OL,6,FThey said this, in turn, can add to a
OL,7,Fworker's "Zoom fatigue" ` a form of
OL,8,Fphysical and mental exhaustion that
OL,9,Fcomes from frequently participating in
OL,10,Fvideo conference calls.
OL,12,FFindings, published in the journal
OL,13,FFrontiers in Psychology, suggest
OL,14,Fpeople who use nature-themed or light-
OL,15,Fhearted backgrounds report having
OL,16,Flower levels of fatigue after online
OL,17,Fmeetings compared with those using
OL,18,Fother types of virtual backdrops or
OL,19,Fnot using any.
