OL,4,Ccall backgrounds
OL,6,FLead author Heng Zhang, a researcher
OL,7,Fat the Nanyang Technological
OL,8,FUniversity Wee Kim Wee School of
OL,9,FCommunication and Information in
OL,10,FSingapore, said: "Image backgrounds
OL,11,Finitially present new information, but
OL,12,Fusers might gradually shift their
OL,13,Fattention elsewhere.
OL,15,F"Blurred backgrounds don't introduce
OL,16,Fnew information, but occasionally
OL,17,Fusers may catch glimpses of the real
OL,18,Fenvironment, which presents new
OL,19,Finformation.
