OL,3,CNew research highlights the best video
OL,4,Ccall backgrounds
OL,6,FPrevious research has shown that
OL,7,Fpeople on video calls spend a lot of
OL,8,Ftime looking at themselves and
OL,9,Fanalysing how they are coming across
OL,10,Fduring the meetings, which can lead to
OL,11,Fmental exhaustion.
OL,13,FFor the current study, the researchers
OL,14,Fcarried out a survey with more than
OL,15,F600 workers aged between 22 and 76 who
OL,16,Fworked from home around three days a
OL,17,Fweek.
