OL,3,CNew research highlights the best video
OL,4,Ccall backgrounds
OL,6,FThe people were asked whether they
OL,7,Fused virtual backgrounds, and if so,
OL,8,Fwhether they used a static image, a
OL,9,Fblurred image, or video backdrops.
OL,11,FA five-point scale was used to measure
OL,12,Fgeneral, visual, social, motivational,
OL,13,Fand emotional fatigue.
OL,15,FThe team found more than seven out of
OL,16,F10 people used a virtual background
OL,17,Fduring video calls, with still images
OL,18,Fbeing the most favoured choice.
