OL,3,CNew research highlights the best video
OL,4,Ccall backgrounds
OL,6,FAmong those using still images, nature-
OL,7,Fthemed ones were the most popular,
OL,8,Ffollowed by interior spaces and
OL,9,Fworkplace photos.
OL,11,FA minority of people opted for
OL,12,Fabstract images and light-hearted
OL,13,Fbackgrounds, the researchers said.
OL,15,FThey said those who said they used
OL,16,F"funny" backgrounds reported lower
OL,17,Fvideo call fatigue than people using
OL,18,Fnature-based backgrounds.
