OL,3,CNew research highlights the best video
OL,4,Ccall backgrounds
OL,6,FThe researchers said this may be
OL,7,Fbecause these types of Zoom
OL,8,Fbackgrounds are not used to impress
OL,9,Fcolleagues.
OL,11,FThe authors wrote: "Individuals who
OL,12,Fuse them may care very little about
OL,13,Fhow these backgrounds portray them, or
OL,14,Fuse these backgrounds simply as a way
OL,15,Fto conceal their actual physical
OL,16,Fenvironment.
OL,18,F"The resultant lack of stress
OL,19,Fassociated with managing their image
OL,20,Fleads to lower videoconferencing
OL,21,Ffatigue."
