OL,6,FMr Zhang added: "Other backgrounds,
OL,7,Fsuch as office settings or public
OL,8,Fspaces can increase users' pressure to
OL,9,Fself-present as if they actually were
OL,10,Fin one of those settings, leading to
OL,11,Fincreased fatigue.
OL,13,F"In a work setting, a nature-themed
OL,14,Fimage background might be the ideal
OL,15,Fchoice."
